DataElement.preferredName: Human Papilloma Virus Vaccine Quality of Life Reduced Problem Other Sexually Transmitted Disorder Assessment Score
DataElement.preferredDefinition: the assessment relating to the subjective measurement of an individual's sense of well-being and ability to enjoy life as it related to less of problem with other sexually transmitted diseases with the recombinant vaccine of different types of HPV proteins which are well-conserved within types with a significant inter-type variation.
